{"tid":614811,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"點解猶太人係歐洲保留到，係中國就全面漢化晒？","createTime":"2018-04-03T00:27:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-03T05:18:30.000Z","uid":57376,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"96a90eddc39b56efd515164529a9435bfdc1ab04","tid":614811,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:27:02.000Z","msg":"歐洲迫害左上千年都同化唔到班人<br />\n中國乜都無做，由你自生自滅，班友反而同化晒，食豬肉，講中文，唔行割禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到底係古中國太好生活環境定點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0314b182b5e6e1bd055800826544ed1b67081519","tid":614811,"uid":174084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:33:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最有錢同能力既猶太人去左美國講英文<br />\n<br />\n留底既都無乜用"},{"pid":"4bce91027fb85a694c90574f6275f6dd255c3660","tid":614811,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"猶太教唔食豬肉㗎咩？"},{"pid":"f66795c04ab6ab344a04442810e95b7c7ddd7f45","tid":614811,"uid":73392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bce91027fb85a694c90574f6275f6dd255c3660","tid":614811,"uid":48796,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:45:47.000Z","msg":"猶太教唔食豬肉㗎咩？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T00:49:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"712801b3642bcc4bffabfe1e652d488a25cce721","tid":614811,"uid":158270,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:04:19.000Z","msg":"猶太人喺歐洲被歧視、孤立，要同其他猶太人通婚，生出嚟嘅自然係猶太人；喺中國人就被接納，同漢族通婚、融合，後代唔再係純正猶太人血統。"},{"pid":"3883509daf2ec9ae339637d59e5365fdd7fea7a7","tid":614811,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-03T03:24:12.000Z","msg":"因為五花腩太好食"},{"pid":"e707f66d35e95092860179146b50ad8051fe36d2","tid":614811,"uid":40216